Just wanted to say, I implemented this change and it did really speed things up! Thanks a bunch :) This is the query I went with:<p><pre><code>  SELECT d.id, d.meta FROM (
    SELECT id FROM data_rows, to_tsquery(&#x27;query&#x27;) AS q
    WHERE tsv @@ q ORDER BY ts_rank_cd(tsv, q) DESC LIMIT 5
  ) AS ids INNER JOIN data_rows d ON d.id = ids.id;
</code></pre>
You can see it in action here on the top right: <a href="https://lateral.io/visualiser/ted" rel="nofollow">https://lateral.io/visualiser/ted</a>
